        <h5 class="card-title">Live Demo — Script Include</h5>
        <p>Click to dynamically load the Moment.js library. The shim appends a <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag to the document head — the same effect as <code>RegisterClientScriptInclude</code> in Web Forms.</p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2 align-items-center flex-wrap">
